


Manual cases:
Page is displayed as expected and headers (for locations, jobs etc) are displayed properly.
All location  links are functioning properly
For every location verify that the the drop-down filtered jobs by department / search string
For the main page verify that the drop-down filtered jobs by location / department / open -search
For every job, verify that that more text is displayed properly when key > pressed.
For every job, verify that when extra text is opened you can email / close it. 
Verify that the easy-helper on right button is opened as expected
Verify that you can upload files to the easy-helper on right button is opened as expected
Verify that the Resume-upload is functioning properly
Verify the Home button is working